During project installation; somme error problem could be revealed related 
to some missing Php extention wich could missed in your System.
To fix it, you have to run some commands to install the missed some php extentions:

Install mbstring php extention : sudo apt-get install php7.0-mbstring

Install dom extention : sudo apt-get install php-xml

Install xml- RPC : sudo apt-get install php7.0-xmlrpc
